  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"traditional\"><p id=\"ubd526e34\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">文本绘图是语雀提供的一种语法绘图，通过一些特定的语法快速绘制出你需要的流程图、甘特图等。目前支持：</span></p><p id=\"u01343157\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u88c05760\"><span class=\"ne-text\">PlantUML</span></li><li id=\"uc0702044\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Mermaid</span></li><li id=\"u078a5149\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Flowchart</span></li><li id=\"uec2787dc\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Graphviz</span></li><li id=\"u86e385f8\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Gantt</span></li></ul><p id=\"u4232d9d4\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ueb7efb24\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"uceb6a53e\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"aeedb111\"><span class=\"ne-text\">插入方式</span></h3><p id=\"u3e36ec0f\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u4761ae33\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击工具栏插入图标选择文本绘图，或输入</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/文本绘图</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或者 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/huitu</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">  快捷键方式插入，支持中文，拼音。</span></p><p id=\"u03e64095\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u11ac335e\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634181750557-da468a68-ac6b-45cc-aa19-b225624e131f.png\" width=\"960\" id=\"u94121953\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uc8f08692\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ud2e8314e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">然后在插入的输入框里选择你需要的语法，输入你对应的语法内容，点击右边预览即可查看你的图片。点击保存后语法代码会转化成图片显示。</span></p><p id=\"u98f54495\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/84147/1555402676177-e8085128-da40-4f19-994e-856284f9745b.png\" width=\"788\" id=\"k8P1B\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h3 id=\"QiDB0\"></h3><h3 id=\"JBFgU\"><span class=\"ne-text\">实时分屏预览</span></h3><p id=\"ua301b28b\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"uf15071cf\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在卡片左侧选择「全屏」，即可实时分屏预览</span></p><p id=\"u7c3f8ea6\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634181877356-bbdd7785-2dd8-42ae-86e5-3cc948d06883.png\" width=\"728\" id=\"u3efa76d3\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u1dbf0263\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634181900340-65690503-065b-4ab4-942b-56e26729c1db.png\" width=\"600\" id=\"u7acf3c35\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u22a2dac0\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u2da54ac0\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u8bc0b15d\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ud214864c\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u959e7c64\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">， 感谢你的支持！</span></p></div>",
  "slug": 13900835,
  "title": "如何插入文本绘图"
}